On Mon, Jul 28, 2025 at 4:20 PM Jack Bear <jack@conversiondigital.com.au> wrote:
Hi Corbin,

  1. Log in to Google Tag Manager.
  2. Click on the relevant container (your website).
  3. In the left-hand menu, go to Admin.
  4. Under the User Management section, click + (top right) and select Add users.
  5. Add our email: access1@conversiondigital.com.au
  6. Under permissions, please tick Admin so we can both view and publish tags.
  7. Click Invite.
Also here is a good video you can follow: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhDZk2vH6-o&t=6s

Let me know if you have any questions.

Thanks,

Jack
